---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Client Intake - The WEL Foundation">
  <div class="container" style="padding: var(--spacing-8) 0; max-width: 900px; text-align: center;">
    <h1 class="reveal-on-scroll" style="color: var(--color-primary-blue); font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">Begin Your Recovery Journey</h1>
    <p class="reveal-on-scroll stagger-1" style="font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6); color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.6; max-width: 700px; margin-inline: auto;">
      Taking the first step is often the hardest. Our streamlined, confidential intake process ensures that you are paired with the right clinical professionals and community resources immediately.
    </p>

    <div class="card reveal-on-scroll stagger-2" style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6); padding: var(--spacing-6);">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4); color: var(--color-primary-light-blue); text-align: center;">What to Expect</h2>
      
      <div class="grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: var(--spacing-5); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">
        <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--spacing-3);">
          <div style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-accent-gold);">1</div>
          <div>
            <h4 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-1);">Submit the Form</h4>
            <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.5;">Fill out our HIPAA-compliant, secure web form. It only takes about 5 minutes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--spacing-3);">
          <div style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-accent-gold);">2</div>
          <div>
            <h4 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-1);">Coordination Call</h4>
            <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.5;">An intake specialist will call you within 24-48 hours to confirm benefits and schedule an assessment.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--spacing-3);">
          <div style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-accent-gold);">3</div>
          <div>
            <h4 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-1);">Clinical Assessment</h4>
            <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.5;">Meet with a licensed counselor to map out your personalized recovery architecture.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: var(--color-bg-offset); padding: var(--spacing-4); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">
        <h4 style="color: var(--color-primary-blue); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2);">Preparation Checklist</h4>
        <ul style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: var(--spacing-4); line-height: 1.6;">
          <li>A clear digital copy (photo or PDF) of your state-issued Government ID.</li>
          <li>A clear digital copy of your current Maryland Medicaid or Private Insurance card.</li>
          <li>Basic contact information and program preferences.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="/intake/start/" class="btn" style="padding: 1rem 2.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">Access Secure Intake Form</a>
        <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-2); font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-text-muted);">Transmitted via encrypted AES-256 connections.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
